IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Cassidee SLIGER and Joseph Sliger Upon the Petition of Cassidee Sliger, n/k/a Cassidee Parks, Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Joseph Sliger, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-0458 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The father appeals the denial of his petition to modify his child-support obligation. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
